---
title: Zesty Pork Chops with Summer Corn & Red Bean Salad
description: Lime, Cajun seasoning, and a honey glaze give these pork chops serious flavor. If you can, throw the chops on the grill for swoon-worthy grill marks. This salad is great warm or cold—perfect for outdoor entertaining!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/zesty-pork-chops-82def65d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/zesty-pork-chops-974f7364.pdf
